Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be performed after SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average cycle time of SW-EIC Reject across all process variants ending with this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-EIC Reject and the end of the case

Name: Time elapsed from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-EIC Reject in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-EIC Reject following a sequence that includes SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-EIC Reject in rejected manuscripts
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time from SW-Checklist Completed to SW-EIC Reject in variants where the review process was initiated (i.e., SW-Reviewer Agreed appears)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-EIC Reject after the last occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time between Plagiarism Originality Report Completed and SW-EIC Reject in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed is present
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Cycle time of SW-EIC Reject compared to the duration of SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in rejection paths
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be executed after the first SW-AE Assign Reviewers activity in rejection variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-EIC Reject in traces containing SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-EIC Reject across all variants that end in rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'
